title: BRIEF-Fingerprint Cards touch sensor included in Meizu's new smartphone
text:
BRIEF-Fingerprint Cards touch sensor included in Meizu's new smartphone Sept 23 
Sept 23 Fingerprint Cards AB 
* Fingerprint Cards touch fingerprint sensor FPC1155 in Meizu's smartphone Pro 5 
* Says already received as well as expected revenues in 2015 that relate to sales of FPC1155 for this smartphone model are included in FPC's communicated revenue guidance of approximately 2,500 MSEK for 2015 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
